# CerebraUI Backend Test Suite

A comprehensive test framework for the CerebraUI backend, featuring intelligent image generation testing with full coverage of prompt analysis, API integration, and end-to-end workflows.

## Test Results

```
Total Tests: 39/39 (100% passing)
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Unit Tests:        16 passed
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Integration Tests:  7 passed
в”ңв”Җв”Җ Performance Tests:  5 passed
в””в”Җв”Җ E2E Tests:         11 passed
```

## Quick Start

```bash
# Run all tests
./run_tests.sh all

# Run specific test suite
./run_tests.sh unit
./run_tests.sh integration
./run_tests.sh performance
./run_tests.sh e2e

# Quick development tests (unit + smoke)
./run_tests.sh quick

# Full suite with coverage
./run_tests.sh full

# CI/CD mode
./run_tests.sh ci
```

## Test Structure

